snippet.title: Daniel Stringer
snippet.description:
Learn to make your own games! 

I will show you my processes for creating games using Unity! from 3D art to coding using C#.

My channel has a strong focus on virtual & augmented reality and using the latest in techniques for creating stunning VR games!
